{"tid":159733,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[本土二五仔] 踢爆地區組織「假本土真泛民」真面目","createTime":"2017-03-17T08:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T16:09:21.000Z","uid":25334,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45b04197c6bc97c378848b36b5a57a1dc6532ce1","tid":159733,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:13:25.000Z","msg":"之前我喺第二個post講過將軍澳青年力量做過好多仆街嘢，比班將青力網軍洗走晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日巴打我攞夠證據屌柒佢哋，唔該班打手自動收皮！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YQ4yb44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYQ4yb44.png&h=406a1ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個個屌緊公民黨唔等PopVote就做決定，呢個組織竟然走去屌民建聯，幫公民黨保駕護航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pzg3PuD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpzg3PuD.png&h=0152717e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被人追問仲要淨係話公民黨係思慮不周，賣埋個屎忽比公民黨吖，垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idvg12O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fidvg12O.png&h=01310adb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逆民意而行，唔屌柒高樓價之餘仲鼓吹樓市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢啲「假本土真泛民」嘅地區組織害人害物，欺騙本土派支持者，大家千祈唔好信佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e10eedaab4f0570759c3a207e2dba44d5f7dae2","tid":159733,"uid":62579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:04:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31366cf7d4dc34a9751972e9706782b0d42490f8","tid":159733,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"